  "text": "Power-law degree distribution. The degree distribution in the Internet topology has been shown to follow a truncated power-law, with few very well-connected nodes, while the majority of nodes have only few connections [CITATION_1] . The well connected nodes typically reside at the top of the hierarchy.",
